-- Bombardier Says Developing New Business Jet Will Cost More Than $1 Billion
-- B y   R a c h e l   L a y n e
-- 2010-10-19T13:46:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-19/bombardier-says-developing-new-business-jet-will-cost-more-than-1-billion.html
Bombardier Inc. said the development
costs for its new Global 7000 and Global 8000 jets will be
“north of” $1 billion.  The figure was disclosed during a briefing for analysts
today by Bombardier Aerospace President Guy Hachey, said
Danielle Boudreau, a spokeswoman.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rachel Layne in Boston at 
 rlayne@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
